erties or in the\ninterpretation of quantum mechanics, and the Rabi-rotating vortices they yield\nshould lead to interesting applications such as ultrafast optical tweezers.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 8 Jan 2018 17:42:06 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 17 Apr 2020 16:08:17 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 11 Apr 2021 23:33:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-04-13"}
