lar geometry in normal pulsars. We believe the\nperiod dependence is a result of an yet unexplained physical phenomenon.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 8 Jan 2018 23:33:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 12 Jan 2018 08:50:50 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 17 Jan 2018 23:52:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-02-28"}
